136
00:06:17,335 --> 00:06:19,170
-Psych! [laughs]
-Dude!

137
00:06:19,253 --> 00:06:21,381
Whatever, man.
Your nuts miss me. I could tell.

138
00:06:21,464 --> 00:06:24,258
