182
00:08:18,498 --> 00:08:22,835
Mohan, you know,
he was so honest and so kind,

183
00:08:22,919 --> 00:08:26,589
and when we moved here
he made me feel closer to my family,

184
00:08:26,672 --> 00:08:29,217
even though we were thousands
of miles away.

185
00:08:31,219 --> 00:08:32,136
He was my rock.

186
00:08:33,596 --> 00:08:36,766
[inhales deeply]
Prashant does remind me of home.

187
00:08:36,849 --> 00:08:37,850
It's nice.

188
00:08:37,934 --> 00:08:40,144
Listen, no one's making you
get married tomorrow,

189
