226
00:10:25,708 --> 00:10:27,376
-Yes.
-Sure. I could totally do that.

227
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:31,339
Good, because it would be
very mature of you.

228
00:10:31,422 --> 00:10:34,425
It would be, and that is why
I'm going to do exactly that.

229
00:10:34,508 --> 00:10:36,135
I'm sure you will.

230
00:10:36,761 --> 00:10:39,847
Guess what, you jealous bitches. I heard
